articles.title: Asian Paints Q4 Results: Profit jumps 45% YoY to Rs 1,234 crore, beats estimates - Economic Times
articles.description: The company's board has recommended payment of a final dividend of Rs 21.25 for the financial year ended March 2023.
articles.content: Asian Paints on Thursday said its consolidated net profit rose 45% year-on-year (YoY) to Rs 1,234 crore in the fourth quarter of FY23. It was Rs 850 crore in the corresponding quarter of last year.Th… [+2420 chars]
